[SN]TITLE[SN]
Girl on scooter seriously hurt in Kilmarnock car crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An 11-year-old girl is being treated in hospital for suspected serious injuries after being struck by a car as she rode a scooter in Kilmarnock.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened in the town's Shortlees Crescent at about 08:30.
The girl was taken by ambulance to Crosshouse Hospital.
The driver of the car was not injured.
